    <h2>What's so special about this package?</h2>
    <p>Localization Helpers is a set of tools to help you manage translations with in your Laravel application. It's parses all translations in application directory and builds the appropriate language files. It also provides an import and export option. Which can be used with external translation services.</p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <p>This package provides tools for the following, and more:</p>

    <ul>
        <li>Remove obsolete translations</li>
        <li>Find and add new or missing translations</li>
        <li>Export/Import CSV & JSON format</li>
        <li>Export/Import to OneSky</li>
        <li>Create backups</li>
    </ul>

